meanings: (특정 장소로) enter, go[get, come] in(to), walk[step] in(to)
(학교·회사 등에) enter, go into; (회사에) be employed; (가입하다) join
(속담) Nothing ventured, nothing gained. or He who would search for pearls, must dive below.

meanings.meaning: Glory is the fair child of peril.
